New cookie business alert ‼️Jess from @leventhalbakery started a home bakery creating thick & gooey delicious cookies! There are currently five flavors: Classic (chocolate chip), Birthday, Dark Chocolate, S'mores, and Peanut Butter. All were incredible but our favorite was Birthday! Go check her out now 🍪

The 8th annual Greenwich Restaurant Week returns Monday, March 27 – Sunday, April 2nd! Join us on March 28th for the Opening Night Party @jhousegreenwich! Tickets include curated cocktails, wine, beer and lite bites from popular Greenwich restaurants like our favorite @hinokigreenwich! Event details, participating restaurants and tickets at 👉GreenwichRestaurantWeek.com

Fried chicken and champagne? Sign us up! We loved trying @walrusalley’s new menu. This brick-walled tavern in downtown Westport has the same owner (and delicious food!) as the old Walrus & Carpenter in Black Rock! Stop by to satisfy all of your barbecue cravings 🍗

social_posts.post_text: Golden hour is back @primestamford

We are SO excited about @diginn expanding to Connecticut👏 Last night we tried their newest location in Stamford (set to open April 24th!). DIG’s menu is scratch-cooked, featuring nourishing foods like the freshest vegetables of the season (we loved the sheet tray carrots!). The restaurant offers lunch and dinner daily and brunch on the weekends (with beer and wine options!). We can’t wait to visit again soon!

@vanleeuwenicecream is opening their second CT location tomorrow, 4/27 in Darien Commons! They’ve teamed up with our favorite @flourwatersaltbread on a limited edition bombolini (Italian doughnut) ice cream sandwich that is a must try! Stop by the grand opening tomorrow for $1 scoops from 3-5🍦

Today is the grand opening of @thegranolabar Darien! Featuring day-to-night dining and a sophisticated vibe, @thegranolabar Darien will be open 7 days a week for breakfast and lunch, and will be open for dinner Tuesday-Saturday! We can’t wait to stop in again soon for more Truffle & Wild Mushroom Pappardelle 🍝

Summer weather is here to stay and the @fortinayachtclub is officially open 👏 The poolside inspired menu features burgers, Sicilian slices, truffle grilled cheeses, and specialty cocktails! Check them out Wed-Fri: 4PM – Close and Sat-Sun: 11AM – Close!

If you haven’t tried @casamecafe what are you waiting for? Authentic Italian food, delicious cocktails, and a stunning space. The Mafaldine Al Limone (lemon zest, parmigiano, crispy capers, aromatic breadcrumbs) is a must try summer dish!

TGIF! It’s a beautiful weekend for a raspberry-lime margarita @donmemowestport 🌮

Pictured:
1) Raspberry-lime margarita, Avocado margarita 
2) Avocado (lime, herbs, green chili)
3) Yellowtail Aquachilie (mango-aji amarillo, platanos, piptizia)
4) Tacos Americanos (soft + crispy, carne molida, cabbage slaw)

The sun is shining and it’s the perfect day for an Espresso Martini or Aperol Spritz from @islaandco 🍾☕️ You also must try the Kangaroo Tucker! (traditional Australian rubbed Kangaroo skewered over herbed tahini, marinated cucumbers, pickled onions, fried lentils)

We are so excited that @seamores, the NYC-based sustainable seafood restaurant group, will open a location in Darien Commons on June 9th! The restaurant will be open for dinner Wednesday-Sunday and will expand to offer dinner every night plus lunch,  brunch, and happy hour this summer!

Pictured:
1) Passionfruit Margarita (lunazul reposado, passion fruit, carpano antica, licor 43, lime, orange bitters)
2) Kale & Avocado Salad (walnuts, sweet potato, quinoa, honey-apple vinaigrette) and Spicy Tuna Crispy Rice 
3) Half Dozen Oyster of the Day (Dutch Island, Jamestown, RI)
4) The Reel Deal (blackened shrimp, rosemary butternut squash spaetzle, creamed spinach)
5) Scallop and Sun Dried Tomato Pasta (GF fusilli, mushrooms, spinach, red onions, grape tomatoes, sun-dried tomato puree)
MŌLÌ, modern & chic Chinese dining experience! 🥢🍸
Incredible meal and experience @goosefeatherny!

MAMAN GREENWICH is here {98 Greenwich Ave!}. We are so excited about NYC’s beloved French Bakery & Cafe to open up their first CT location right here in Greenwich!

Pictured:
1) Nutty chocolate chip cookie (fan-favorite cookie filled with macadamia nuts, almonds, walnuts, & dark chocolate wafers, featured on oprah’s favorite things!)
2) Paris to New York croissant (decadent chocolate cookie nestled inside a croissant, topped with layers of hazelnut chocolate spread, white corn chocolate, & crushed hazelnuts)
3) Boardwalk sea salt caramel iced latte (sea salt caramel sauce, cold milk, parlor’s merci espresso, whip & caramel corn pieces)
4) Honey lavender latte (double shot of espresso paired with our honey lavender syrup & served with milk)
@naya Darien Commons is now open! We are so excited to have authentic Middle Eastern cuisine right here in Darien! The perfect spot to build your own roll, bowl, or salad for lunch this week 🌯

We finally tried THE🐔sandwich at @havenhotchicken Norwalk, CT and it did not disappoint! We are so lucky to have Nashville-style Hot Chicken right here in Fairfield county 🍗

Pictured: THE Sandwich (Buttermilk-marinated, boneless chicken breast, creamy vinegar slaw, garlic-dill pickle, Rob Sauce, on a toasted Martin’s® potato bun)

@greersoutherntable is now open in Norwalk, CT! Greer offers elevated pub fare with a southern flare. We highly recommend stopping in for their new weekend brunch! 

Pictured:
1) Highbrow Nosh Board (highbrow & pimento cheese spreads, house-pickled onions, jalapeños & pickles, bacon jam, tomato jam, crudités, Muffuletta olive spread, thinly sliced Tasso, herbed butter, crusty baguette, Ritz crackers)
2) Bacon Bloody Mary (bacon vodka, bacon salt rim, candied bacon garnish)
3) Southern Nicoise (herbed salmon, hard boiled eggs, fingerling potatoes, haricot vert, muffalatta olive spread, capers, red wine shallot vinaigrette)
4) Roasted Cauliflower Steak (char grilled cauliflower, benne seed puree, toasted walnut-caper salsa)
5) House-made Maple Bacon Doughnuts (maple icing, warm bacon bits)
The Beach: BEC + avocado & hot sauce 🍳

‼️$100 GIVEAWAY‼️ NAME THIS COCKTAIL 
@thevillagewheel & @ct_sprinkles have teamed up to create a signature cocktail available for a limited time only @thevillagewheel 🍸 The winner gets a $100 gift card to @thevillagewheel and we need your help naming it!

This Fall inspired speciality cocktail will pop-up on the bar menu this Friday, September 8th and will be available through the end of October! 

A percentage of proceeds from the sale of the drink will also benefit @nokidhungry - a charity organization that aims to end childhood hunger in the U.S.

Ingredient list is below for inspo!

Ketel One Vodka 
Freshly Squeezed Lime Juice 
Apple Cider 
Ginger Beer
Cinnamon Syrup
Topped w/ @theowlsbrew Spiced Chai & Cranberry 
Cinnamon Stick Garnish 

To enter: 
1. Like this post 
2. Follow @thevillagewheel & @ct_sprinkles 
3. Tag a friend in the comments 
4. Comment with your suggested cocktail name 

***ONLY ONE ENTRY PER ACCOUNT***

Contest ends Thursday, September 7th at 11:59PM EST. 

Open to US residents only; age 18 and up. This giveaway is not sponsored, endorsed, administered by or associated with Instagram.

A GHOUL’S MULE!🍸🍎 Now available @thevillagewheel beginning this evening through the end of October! 

Congrats to our winner @alyssatrip 👏🏻

A percentage of proceeds from the sale of the drink will benefit @nokidhungry, so be sure to join us this fall season and have a cocktail for a cause!🍁🤩
